  "text": "In the present study, the behavioral results showed that 7 times of WM at ST25 and ST37 significantly attenuated CRDinduced CVH in IBS-like rats, which is consistent with our previous studies [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] . It should be mentioned that WM treatment in the present and previous animal studies only partially inhibited CVH. This may be due to the fact that WM treatment in animal studies only involves stimulation of two acupoints, which also supports the clinical usage of multiple acupoints.",
